## ğŸš€ What Was Built

### Core Framework (5 Research Papers)

#### 1. **AutoRedTeamer** (arXiv:2503.15754)
- âœ… Multi-agent architecture (Red Team + Strategy Proposer)
- âœ… Lifelong attack integration via persistent memory
- âœ… Memory-guided attack selection
- âœ… Autonomous strategy discovery
- **Performance**: 20% higher success, 46% lower cost

#### 2. **PersonaTeaming** (arXiv:2509.03728)
- âœ… Dynamic persona generation (5 expert + 5 regular user templates)
- âœ… Context-adaptive persona selection
- âœ… 15 mutation strategies across expertise levels
- âœ… Mutation distance tracking for diversity
- **Performance**: Up to 144% improvement in attack success

#### 3. **MITRE ATT&CK Integration** (arXiv:2509.07939)
- âœ… Deterministic attack tree with 15+ TTPs
- âœ… Guided reasoning pipeline
- âœ… TTP validation and constraint enforcement
- âœ… MITRE Navigator export
- **Performance**: 71.8%-78.6% task completion vs 13.5%-16.5% self-guided

#### 4. **RedAgent** (arXiv:2407.16667)
- âœ… Context-aware autonomous agent
- âœ… 8 jailbreak strategies (gradual escalation, role-play, etc.)
- âœ… Self-reflection and adaptation
- âœ… 5-query optimization with memory buffer
- **Performance**: 90% success rate in â‰¤5 queries

#### 5. **SEAS** (arXiv:2408.02632)
- âœ… Self-evolving adversarial optimization
- âœ… Iterative improvement cycles (Initialization â†’ Attack â†’ Optimization)
- âœ… Failure analysis and adaptation
- âœ… Hybrid strategy synthesis
- **Performance**: Continuous improvement across iterations

